# Form handling

- RHF + Zod (`zodResolver`); same schema in server action (Zod v4 — see `zod-v4.mdc`).
- Schemas from `@/actions/.../[action].validation.ts` only — never in components.
- `mode: "onChange"`; disable submit when invalid or submitting.
- Required: `<span className="text-destructive">*</span>` on label.
- Select optional: `"--"` not `""`; map to `null`.
- FormDescription: `className="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500"`.
- Errors: `fieldState` → FormItem `border-destructive/50 bg-destructive/5 p-2`; input `border-destructive focus-visible:ring-destructive`.
- Error summary above submit with i18n labels.

Ref: `storeAdmin` edit dialogs + validation colocated with actions.
